		<h2>Usige Bàn Falls</h2>
		<p>
A 1.5 kilometre round trip hike to a spectacular 15 m waterfall. Picnic tables and pit toilets are available. Located 14.5 kilometres (9 miles) north of Baddeck.
		</p>
